Hi,

I'm attempting a refactoring of the SharpNEAT code base, converting
the code to use generics (The dotNet world's name for templates) and
generally just cleaning it up. It's not a working version yet as there
is no evolution algorithm class but there is a NeatGenome,
RecurrentNetwork and a bunch of generic interface classes with
documentation tags that roughly outline how it's all going to fit
together. I'll be placing copies on a public URL in case anyone wants
to take a peek and provide feedback.

The URL is:

http://www.cgreen.dsl.pipex.com/

Regards,

Colin.
